<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 16:07:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列必须粉碎哈马斯，推翻它的权力。然后呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-smash-hamas-topple-it-from-power-then-what/0000018b-0f67-d3a8-afeb-8f6f0fc10000</link><description>领导力的根本失败。灾难性的情报和行动失败。那么什么才能将这场灾难转化为以色列的胜利呢？</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 15:27:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-smash-hamas-topple-it-from-power-then-what/0000018b-0f67-d3a8-afeb-8f6f0fc10000</guid></item><item><title>这就是对以色列的袭击成为可能的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-what-made-the-attack-on-israel-possible/0000018b-0fb9-d2fb-a3df-cfbd13b70000</link><description>与 1973 年的战争不同，2023 年的失败是系统性的：表现为情报的缺乏、军队的反应不充分以及政治领导的缺失</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 15:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-what-made-the-attack-on-israel-possible/0000018b-0fb9-d2fb-a3df-cfbd13b70000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：美国正在核实数名美国人在哈马斯“恐怖”袭击中丧生和失踪的报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-u-s-verifying-reports-of-several-americans-killed-missing-in-terrorist-attack/0000018b-0f72-dcc2-a99b-1f7387ad0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯称这次袭击是“1973年赎罪日战争以来最严重的一次”，并强调这一次是“恐怖袭击，枪杀了以色列平民的城镇和家园”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 14:36:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-u-s-verifying-reports-of-several-americans-killed-missing-in-terrorist-attack/0000018b-0f72-dcc2-a99b-1f7387ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯在加沙扣押了数十人。释放他们仍然是一个难以捉摸的挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-dozens-of-captives-held-in-gaza-freeing-them-remains-an-elusive-challenge/0000018b-0f62-dfff-a7eb-affac4440000</link><description>俘虏的令人心碎的视频可能会增加公众推动达成释放协议的压力，但历史告诉我们，这可能需要数年时间。据知情人士透露，以色列的大部分国际努力都集中在获得在加沙实施大规模袭击的合法性，而不是释放人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 14:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-dozens-of-captives-held-in-gaza-freeing-them-remains-an-elusive-challenge/0000018b-0f62-dfff-a7eb-affac4440000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的防御在哈马斯的袭击下崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/six-significant-failures-that-lead-to-one-point-collapse-vs-hamas/0000018b-0f15-dfff-a7eb-afdd0bb80000</link><description>以色列完全措手不及，花了很长时间才将部队运送到战场以保卫遭受攻击的地区。这是决定战斗发展的六个主要失败</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 13:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/six-significant-failures-that-lead-to-one-point-collapse-vs-hamas/0000018b-0f15-dfff-a7eb-afdd0bb80000</guid></item><item><title>问答：以色列遭遇火箭弹袭击或恐怖袭击时我该怎么办？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/q-a-what-should-i-do-during-a-rocket-strike-in-israel/0000018b-0f27-dcc2-a99b-1f37cbe80000</link><description>加沙火箭袭击期间住在哪里最安全？我可以离开这个国家吗？如何找到失踪人员？是否有英语求助热线？</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/q-a-what-should-i-do-during-a-rocket-strike-in-israel/0000018b-0f27-dcc2-a99b-1f37cbe80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列死亡：平民、士兵和紧急服务人员在与哈马斯的战争中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/israels-dead-civilians-soldiers-emergency-services-personnel-killed-in-war-with-hamas/0000018b-0de8-dc5d-a39f-9fecb5a30000</link><description>哈马斯